    "This reflects ENMA's ability to generate high-fidelity samples that are well-aligned with physical ground truth.",
    "In terms of Precision, ENMA also outperforms Zebra, demonstrating superior sample quality.",
    "However, Zebra obtains a higher Recall, suggesting that it covers a broader range of modes from the data distribution.",
    "This highlights a trade-off: ENMA prioritizes fidelity and realism, whereas Zebra exhibits slightly more diversity, potentially at the cost of precision.",
    "Overall, these results illustrate ENMA's strength in producing high-quality, physically plausible trajectories, while maintaining reasonable diversity in its generative predictions."
